            SET project_id = ?, session_name = ?, session_type = ?, initial_prompt = ?, context_data = ?,
                generated_ideas = ?, selected_ideas = ?, session_notes = ?, model_used = ?, total_tokens = ?,
                cost_credits = ?, status = ?, updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
            WHERE id = ?
